CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FA medical student who lost all four
OL,7,Flimbs to Sepsis after contracting
OL,8,FMeningitis B says that, following
OL,9,Finitial anger, she is not "resentful",
OL,10,Fdespite finding out she was
OL,11,Funvaccinated against the bacteria.
OL,13,FLily McGarry, 24 and from Jersey, says
OL,14,Fshe feels lucky to be alive following
OL,15,Ftwo cardiac arrests and spending three
OL,16,Fmonths in a coma.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FThe quick actions of her housemates,
OL,7,Fwho took her to A&E in January last
OL,8,Fyear as her condition quickly
OL,9,Fdeteriorated, are believed to have
OL,10,Fsaved the third-year Cardiff
OL,11,FUniversity student.
OL,13,FLily explains: "Things deteriorated
OL,14,Fvery quickly. I was out in a nightclub
OL,15,Fwith friends on Friday night, we went
OL,16,Ffor a run on Sunday, and on Monday I
OL,17,Fstarted feeling a bit rough but I
OL,18,Fthought maybe I'd just had too busy a
OL,19,Fweekend and was coming down with the
OL,20,Fflu.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,F"I was still able to walk into A&E
OL,7,Fwith help and then, within hours, I
OL,8,Fwas unconscious. It is really scary to
OL,9,Fthink what could have happened had my
OL,10,Fhousemates not come to check on me.
OL,12,F"That's why I really want to encourage
OL,13,Fpeople to look out for each other."
OL,15,FA number of surgeries followed and
OL,16,FLily became a quadruple amputee,
OL,17,Fundergoing extensive and ongoing
OL,18,Ftreatment to help her live as
OL,19,Findependently as possible.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FShe says: "It's been difficult, it's
OL,7,Fbeen a long process to come to terms
OL,8,Fwith things.
OL,10,F"I didn't feel like I was at risk, I
OL,11,Fwas otherwise fit and healthy."
OL,13,FBabies have only received the
OL,14,FMeningitis B vaccination since May
OL,15,F2015, which was too late for people
OL,16,Flike Lily.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FHowever, she has grown to understand
OL,7,Fwhy the UK Government has not yet
OL,8,Frolled out a wider, nationwide
OL,9,FMeningitis B vaccination programme to
OL,10,Fboost protection for young adults, as
OL,11,Fshe recognises there is a complex
OL,12,Fbalance.
OL,14,FLily explains: "It's hard to say what
OL,15,Fthe right thing to do for my age group
OL,16,Fis, but awareness of the symptoms is
OL,17,Fkey because the earlier you catch it,
OL,18,Fthe better your outcomes are likely to
OL,19,Fbe.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,F"I was annoyed when I found out that I
OL,7,Fwas unvaccinated against Meningitis B.
OL,8,FI felt like my age group had been
OL,9,Fignored but the more research I've
OL,10,Fdone, the studies do show that
OL,11,Fantibodies seem to wane after one or
OL,12,Ftwo years post vaccination, so I can
OL,13,Ftry to see why there is an argument
OL,14,Fthat it's not cost-effective.
OL,16,F"It works on such an individual basis,
OL,17,Fit's hard to predict how much immune
OL,18,Fmemory it will generate from one
OL,19,Fperson to the next, so introducing a
OL,20,Fcampaign to vaccinate everyone - it's
OL,21,Fnot like a one-size-fits-all."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FHowever, if someone is offered a
OL,7,Fvaccine, Lily wants them to take it.
OL,9,FShe adds: "I feel quite frustrated
OL,10,Fwhen people think there are perhaps
OL,11,Fhidden agendas or that the Government
OL,12,Fare being too pushy when it comes to
OL,13,Fvaccination, because in my eyes,
OL,14,Fthat's only for our safety.
OL,16,F"It's important that those who can get
OL,17,Fvaccinated do, so they create herd
OL,18,Fimmunity and protect those who can't
OL,19,Ffor various issues like having a
OL,20,Fchronic illness."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FLily has also been reflecting on the
OL,7,FKent meningitis outbreak, which has
OL,8,Fkilled two people and left others
OL,9,Fseriously unwell in hospital.
OL,11,FShe says: "I guess I was just unlucky,
OL,12,Fbut relative to the two students in
OL,13,FKent who have sadly died, I am lucky
OL,14,Fto still be here."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,FSpeaking about that time in January
OL,7,Flast year while studying at Cardiff
OL,8,FUniversity, she adds: "I've thought,
OL,9,F'What if I didn't go out on that
OL,10,FFriday night? Maybe I picked it up
OL,11,Ffrom someone who was dancing around
OL,12,Fme'.
OL,14,F"But then I think, I was doing what a
OL,15,Fnormal 23-year-old student would be
OL,16,Fdoing and unfortunately, it's likely
OL,17,Fto be my genetics that have made me
OL,18,Fsusceptible to the bacteria and that's
OL,19,Flife.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,F"I'm ok and I am getting better, I
OL,7,Fdon't feel resentful."
OL,9,FLily has become an ambassador for the
OL,10,Fcharity Sepsis Research and is
OL,11,Fcommitted to spreading awareness so
OL,12,Fthat others spot the signs early.
OL,14,FShe also now has Sonny, a 12-week-old
OL,15,Fgolden retriever, who is helping with
OL,16,Fher recovery.
OL,18,FShe explains: "It's something I've
OL,19,Fwanted for 24 years. I've always loved
OL,20,Fdogs and it's just really healing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,F"Especially now it's spring, it's a
OL,7,Fgood excuse to get outside. I
OL,8,Fdefinitely get the affection from her.
OL,10,F"Her recall's not great; she'll come
OL,11,Fback if there's not something more
OL,12,Fexciting to look at or sniff.
OL,14,F"It's quite surreal how much things
OL,15,Fhave changed. 2025 just feels like a
OL,16,Fmissed year for me. It's strange
OL,17,Fhaving so much free time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1774458667
OL,3,CUnvaccinated student who lost limbs to
OL,4,CMeningitis shares anger and acceptance
OL,6,F"I'm trying to do things like learn
OL,7,FSpanish and make art with my granny,
OL,8,Fenjoy having time to do things I
OL,9,Fhaven't done before."
OL,11,FFor more about Lily's journey, watch
OL,12,F'Lily McGarry: Life after sepsis as a
OL,13,Fquadruple amputee' on ITVX:
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
